text:
Even though Josh continues to shoot down he and Jennifer are anything more than friends, we can dream can't we?

"It does truly amaze me what some of the things that are printed," the actor tells E! about past rumors they're the next celebrity couple. "It's like, how is that even legal? I try not to comment on it. It is what it is and it's part of the business. We're in the circus and that's part of being in the circus."
title: Jennifer Garner & Josh Duhamel Called the 'Perfect Couple' After He Admits She's an 'Incredible Woman'
